🔺 @Danny_Howells78 has quietly worked his way through the ranks in the world of house music and has continued to make his mark. His organic approach has helped him maintain his position as one of the world’s most captivating selectors. His impeccable selection, distinctive style, and smooth mixing are a testament to his talent.

🔻 In recent years, Danny has released several well-received EPs on Germany’s 8bit label, including ‘Earthlings,’ ‘Shortwave,’ and ‘Dayshift’ on @Selador_Recordings, the label of his long-time friend @DaveSeamandj. Danny has also been touring regularly with Darren Emerson as 3D.

🙌 Danny is scheduled to perform at Selador Recordings’ 10th-anniversary celebration at #ADE on Saturday, October 21, 2023, at Boom Chicago. We had the chance to discuss with him about his upcoming performance, as well as his animal rights activism, volunteering, and future plans.

You can read the full interview now ⏩ link in bio.

Live at the Troubadour with Danny Howells - Interview, Listening Session, DJ Set

Date: Sunday, October 29
Time: 1:30 PM - 5:30 PM
Venue: @troubadourlondon 
Address: 265 Old Brompton Rd, London
Tickets: £10 (only 30 tickets available, link in bio)

I am so incredibly stoked to announce that the next Super Progressive live event will be with @danny_howells78 !!!

The Essential Mixes. Nocturnal Frequencies. Bedrock parties. Renaissance. Nubreed. Global Underground. Balance. Danny’s contributions to the underground are immense, and I’m so excited to host him for this live interview, listen to some tracks that created some iconic moments in his career, and of course a proper DJ set to finish it off. 

Danny is the perfect guest, and the Troubadour is the perfect venue. I am so honored to introduce the music we love, underground dance music, into the storied legacy of the Troubadour. Legendary musicians like Bob Dylan and Jimi Hendrix played their first ever gigs in the UK at the Troubadour, and its been host to other legends like Robert Plant and Jimmy Paige of Led Zeppelin, Charlie Watts, Ronnie Wood and Mick Taylor of The Rolling Stones, Joni Mitchell, Paul Simon, and more more. And now it’s time to add Danny Howells to the list. I’ve always felt like the top progressive underground artists and DJs bring the same sophistication to their music as these rock and roll legends, so hosting this event at the Troubadour makes so much sense to me. 

It’s going to be a very intimate event with an MTV Unplugged vibe, so if you’d like the chance to experience Danny Howells up close and even ask him a question or two, I hope you can join us. There’s a bar in the downstairs venue where we will be and food upstairs, so it should really be a good time. I honestly can’t wait. 

Thank you @danny_howells78 and thank you @troubadourlondon, this is what Super Progressive is all about. 

#progressivehouse #housemusic #dannyhowells #troubadour

Skyline is all about community. We are a family, we come together to celebrate our love of music.

So with Christmas looming and all of us skint, we want to give something back – to our Skyliners and to an amazing local charity.

We are bringing back our first ever guest, the amazing Danny Howells, for a very special January edition of Skyline with FREE entry.

Not only that – he’s playing all night long, a special DIG DEEPER set where we really get to know what makes Danny tick as a DJ, with a 6hr set.

There is one little caveat though – we want you to make a donation in return for a ticket for our free party. The money from those tickets goes to Tribe Animal Sanctuary Scotland, an amazing animal rescue chosen by Danny.

And it’s up to you how much you pay – you can choose to pay £5, £10 or £15. No one will know what you paid, and all the cash goes to Tribe.

As always you can stay over to make a real night of it and it’s our lowest ever room rate – because we want to give you the gift of something to look forward to in January.
For just £90 FOR TWO, we will serve up your overnight stay, welcome drinks and breakfasts…and it includes a £10 donation to TRIBE.

It all goes off on January 28, so join us. You are Skyline. We are Skyline. This is Skyline. 🔥

Tickets on sale NOW! Link in bio.

A cada novo evento, o River Club, localizado na cidade de Montenegro, vem se provando como um dos mais queridos e especiais do Brasil. 

Com uma identidade muito definida, indo do organic house até progressive house, o club completa 7 anos no dia 23 de dezembro apresentando o maior headliner de sua história! Estamos falando de ninguém menos do que o lendário DJ e produtor britânico Danny Howells. 

Já pensou curtir um role com o Danny nesse lindo lugar em meio a natureza?

#progressivehouse #dannyhowells

🔺 In collaboration with EG, @Danny_Howells78 is thrilled to share this unique offering with his fans. The track, named ‘Larus,’ adds a distinct flavor to the British artist’s repertoire, diverging from his previous releases and tailored for after-hours settings.

🗣️ “Thanks to #ElectronicGroove for working with me on getting these two tracks out. Both ‘Mycelium’ and ‘Larus’ are quite different from what I’ve released previously and were really intended to be played in after-hours situations. I had no intention of ever putting them out, but they’re two of the tracks I’m most proud of. I hope some of our followers enjoy it!,” Danny  commented.

🎶 Grab your free track! Link in bio for an exclusive download!

AFTER MOVIE RIVER 7 ANOS! 🏰🪩✨

Não tinha como ser diferente, depois de uma campanha repleta de desafios, fomos agraciados com um diazão de sol e calor, as boas energias e vibrações positivas tomaram conta do Castelo! Foi lindo! 

Um dia para ficar marcado na nossa história e na memória de todos!

Presenciar a lenda Danny Howells dando aula, mantendo a pista conectada e imersa no seu set por 5 horas só comprovou nossas expectativas, foram momentos de pura magia, técnica e talento! Danny sabe o que faz! 

Sarah Chilanti e Elieser fizeram um b2b de alto nível sonoro, uma conexão perfeita para deixar a pista pronta para o mestre Danny! 

Dietz e Lucas Vargas dando o play inicial com fineza e sutileza, convite ideal para pista se entregar ao momento e dar start na celebração! 

Um agradecimento especial ao público que acreditou no evento e se fez presente! 
As pessoas que vieram de outros estados, outra cidades, nosso muito obrigado, isso enche nosso coração de alegria. 

Nosso agradecimento especial também ao staff, equipe de marketing e comunicação do River, fornecedores e administração do @castelo_kebach. 

2023 finalizado com sucesso, que venha o próximo ano com mais histórias incríveis como essa que escrevemos no ultimo sábado! ❤️✨

🎥 @pedrofell_

What an incredible way to end the year.
Huge thanks to @analog__a for putting together yet another amazing tour. I say this every time I visit South America but this has truly been one of the best ever.

Huge thanks of course to the clubs that welcomed and looked after me, and everyone involved in putting these events together. Plus all the wonderful DJs I played alongside and, as always, everyone who came out and partied with us 🙏

Also a massive thank you to @ongpajaroscaidos @leoneldeangelis1 and @claracorrea_pajaroscaidos for helping me with the various pigeons I found that needed some TLC, and also to @gaspicarrenio and the crew in Rosario for putting together the most amazing vegan Christmas dinner and making me feel totally at home with them.

The final stop will be @lajuanitamusic in Punta del Este with @chapa.castelo on New Year’s Day, then it’s back home for some studio time (after a very long gap!) and @skyline_events in Glasgow at the end of the month.

Wishing everyone an amazing 2024 and hopefully see you next year! 💚

3 weeks to go until our 1st Skyline of 2024.

Set times for Skyline presents Danny Howells - Dig Deeper! 

“With a reputation as “the DJs’ DJ”, he has remained stoic in the face of ever-shifting trends and fads in dance music since he broke through into the global house music consciousness in the late-’90s. He doesn’t churn out productions to “remain relevant”, instead only releasing music as and when inspiration strikes. He’s not a publicity hungry, social media devotee. He’s not someone who feels the need to reinvent himself with new monikers or side projects, nor someone who aggressively pursues a maxxed-out DJ’ing schedule. Quietly ploughing his way through the house music continuum, he has remained one of the world’s most captivating selectors precisely because of these organic means. That and his impeccable selection, distinctive style and silky mixing, of course. “ RA

5pm kick off this month, 7pm curfew for the start of Danny’s set. Don’t be late! We’re delighted to be welcoming Super Progressive along to cover the show also. See you on the roof. 💃

Remember all profit from the ticket donations of this show is going to Danny’s nominated charity - Tribe Animal Sanctuary in Glasgow. 

This is Skyline 🔥
